Reporter Lindokuhle Xulu is monitoring this story outside the police station. #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - Operation Dudula leader Nhlanhla 'Lux' Dlamini is spending the weekend in jail. He's calling for calm from his supporters while he remains behind bars. He was arrested on Thursday after a Soweto resident laid charges against him. His lawyers and other Dudula leaders failed to secure his release from police custody. Courtesy #DStv403